title: xNetflix (Clone of Netflix)
description: Full stack application built with complete authentication and authorization. Users can sign-in / sign-up with their email and password or one click authentication provided by google and github. People can watch movies/series and add to thier playlist. Tech Stack: Nextjs, Typescript, MongoDb, Prisma, NextAuth, Google Cloud, Tailwind Css.
